Hey guys!

Dumb Charades, Pictionary, Tinto, Taboo  been a boss at these at every
party you've attended?

Then wait no longer, for Litsoc is back with its mostly lively event,
Litsoc Potpourri, where you'll be treated to these and much more!! Quiz
